                        <msContents>
                            <summary>'Tahẕīb al-Manṭiq va al-Kalām' is a work in logic (Manṭiq) and scholastic theology (Kalām) of Saʿd al-Dīn Masʿūd Taftāzānī (died 792 AH/1390).
                                Two parts of this work have been commented on and annotated since its creation in several works. One of the most important works written on the logic part is
                                Mullā ʻAbd Allāh Yazdī's commentary known as 'Quluhū', which is one of the main textbooks in Shiite seminaries (religious schools).
                            </summary>
                        <msItem>
                            <locus from="1a" to="55a">ff. 1a-55a</locus>
                            <textLang mainLang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                            <note type="content-genre">Islamic logic</note>                            
                            <author key="person_24447170">
                                <persName xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Yazdī, ʻAbd Allāh ibn al-Ḥusayn, -1606 or 1607‏</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara" type="standard">یزدی، عبدالله ابن الحسین، -۱۶۰۶ یا ۱۶۰۷</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Mullā ʻAbd Allāh ibn Ḥusayn Yazdī, -981 AH/-1573‏</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara" type="alt">ملا عبدالله ابن حسین یزدی، -۹۸۱ق/-۱۵۷۳</persName>
                            </author>
                            <title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20515" change="#ids-cleanup">Ḥāshīyah ʿalá Tahẕīb al-Manṭiq</title>
                            <title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20515" type="alt" change="#ids-cleanup">Ḥāshīyah-i Mullā ʿAbd Allāh</title>
                            <title xml:lang="ara" key="work_20515" change="#ids-cleanup">حاشیه علی تهذیب المنطق</title>
                            <title xml:lang="ara" key="work_20515" type="alt" change="#ids-cleanup">حاشیه ملا عبدالله</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="ara" defective="true">… علی انّه ذکر من الوصف بمرتبه لا بتبادر الذهن منه الا… بین الصفات هذه لکونها مستلزمه…
                            </incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="ara">… قوله و هذا بالمقاصد اشبه ایّ الامر الثامن اشبه بمقاصد الفن بمقدماته… و ایاکم من الراسخین فی الامرین و رزقنا الله بفضله و جوده… والحمد لله رب العالمین.
                                </explicit>
                            <colophon xml:lang="ara">قد فرغت من تسوید هذه الرساله الموسومه بحاشیه ملا عبدالله فی اوایل عشر الثانی من شهر الذیحجه الحرام من شهور سنه ۱۱۱۹ و انا العبد… ابن حاج رفیع‌هادی. 
                            </colophon>
