                        <msContents>
                            <summary>
                                This is one of the famous works in Shiite Kalām. The author, upon the request of the minister Muḥammad ibn Muḥammad Qūhadī, summarized into 10 parts the book of 
                                Miṣbāḥ al-Mutahajjid of Shaykh Ṭūsī, and called it Minhāj al-Ṣalāḥ fī Mukhtaṣar al-Miṣbāḥ. He then added to it a further part called Bāb al-Ḥādī ʿAshar on the Principles of Religion
                                to make it complete. Bāb al-Ḥādī ʿAshar was prepared in seven chapters. Chapter one on 'Proving the Creator', chapter two on 'Affirmative attributes', chapter four on Justice,... and chapter seven on Resurrection.
                                There have been many commentaries written on this work, of which one of the most famous works is called al-Nāfīʿ Yawm al-Ḥashr fī Sharḥ al-Bāb al-Ḥādī ʿAshr of Miqdād ibn ʿAbd Allāh Sīvarī Ḥillī.
                                This copy covers from the beginning of the work up to chapter 6, article 3.
                            </summary>
                        <msItem>
                            <locus from="55b" to="58b">ff. 55b-58b</locus>
                            <textLang mainLang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                            <note type="content-genre">Kalām (Islamic Scholastic Theology)</note>
                            <title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" key="work_4296">Bāb-i Ḥādī ʿAshar</title>
                            <title xml:lang="ara" key="work_4296">باب حادی عشر</title>
                            <author key="person_32056992">
                                <persName xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Ibn al-Muṭahhar al-Ḥillī, al-Ḥasan ibn Yūsuf, 1250-1325‏</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Ḥillī, ʿAllāmah Jamāl al-Dīn Abū Manṣūr Ḥasan ibn Sadīd al-Dīn Yūsuf ibn ʿAlī, 648-726 AH/1251-1326‏</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara" type="standard">ابن المطهر الحلی، الحسن ابن یوسف، ۱۲۵۰-۱۳۲۵</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara" type="alt">حلّی، علامه جمال‌الدین ابومنصور حسن بن سدیدالدین یوسف بن علی، ۶۴۸-۷۲۶ق/۱۲۵۱-۱۳۲۶</persName>
                            </author>
                            <incipit xml:lang="ara">بسمله، الباب الحادی عشر فیما یجب علی عامه المکلفین من معرفه اصول‌الدین اجمع العلماء کافه علی وجوب معرفه الله تعالی و صفاته الثبوتیه و السلبیه…
                            </incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="ara" defective="true">… الثالث الامام یجب ان یکون منصوصا علیه لان العصمه من الامور الباطنه التی لا یعلمها الا الله… فلا بد من تعیین…
                            </explicit>
